bvpSolve-package        Solvers for Boundary Value Problems (BVP) of
                        Ordinary Differential Equations
bvpcol                  Solves multipoint boundary value problems of
                        ordinary differential equations or differential
                        algebraic equations, using a collocation
                        method.
bvpshoot                Solver for two-point boundary value problems of
                        ordinary differential equations, using the
                        single shooting method
bvptwp                  Solves two-point boundary value problems of
                        ordinary differential equations, using a
                        mono-implicit Runge-Kutta formula
diagnostics.bvpSolve    Prints Diagnostic Characteristics of BVP
                        Solvers
plot.bvpSolve           Plot and Print Methods for Output of bvp
                        solvers
